## Key design decisions
- Pipeline branching routes by VideoType from signal_assessment
- STOCK_PICK/SECTOR → stock analysis only
- MACRO/NEWS_EVENT/OTHER → macro insights + conditional stock analysis
- MARKET_REVIEW → market review summary + macro insights from review
- EXPERT_INTERVIEW → expert insights + macro + conditional stock analysis
- ExpertInsight uses heuristic regex patterns (no LLM call)
- Combined dashboard deduplicates macro by indicator, stocks by ticker
- Channel analysis auto-generates dashboard file alongside per-video reports
- Pipeline refactored: _run_stock_analysis eliminates 5x duplication
- Heuristic pipeline now has parity with LLM pipeline on VideoType output
- Cache staleness defaults to 7 days; resolve_transcript_text prefers re-fetch over stale

